Time Tracker

Time Tracker is a tool for tracking time in Pivotal Tracker projects. It integrates with PT through the public API.

User sees a list of task in all his projects. He can click play/stop to start/finish working on a task.

Project owners can see detailed reports about all the work done in their projects. Regular users have access only to their own work.

It's tracked here: https://www.pivotaltracker.com/projects/132571

Version: 1.6.1
